project_descr: The immediate objective of the project is to assist the country in the preparation and submission of its First Biennial Update Report to the Conference of the Parties to the UNFCCC.

outputs.output_descr: To assist the Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia in the preparation of its First Biennial Update Report (FBUR) for the fullfilment of the obligations under the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC).

document_name: Macedonian Biennial GHG Emissions Update Report
project_title: macedonian biennial ghg emissions update report
